HTML-FormHandlerX-Form-JQueryValidator
======================================

This perl Trait allows you to re-use some form validation rules with the
 JQuery Validation plugin (http://docs.jquery.com/Plugins/Validation)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  HTML::FormHandler

